description:
Under Pressure



Aired on 02/03/2012, Narrated by Jonathan Aris



On 11 July 1991, Nigeria Airways Flight 2120, a Douglas DC-8-61, is taking off from Jeddah's King Abdulaziz International Airport with 247 Nigerian Hajj pilgrims and 14 crew on board. A tire bursts during the takeoff, starting a fire on the landing gear. The crew are unaware of the fire and retract the gear after take off, and the fire spreads.
